Package uniol.apt.adt Description

Implementation of various abstract data types. This package contains a generic interface for graphs called IGraph. Based on this, the PetriNet and TransitionSystem classes are implemented. Additionally, there is FiniteAutomaton representing a finite automaton. This class does not implement the IGraph interface.
